chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
Yes
awesome! just standing at the starting point here now
Veo una ramita a mi izquierda que conduce a una pequeña isla con un tigre. Entonces, ¿qué camino tomar, amigo?
Go past the tiger and large rock. You will see a stick, cross the stick until you see a parrot
got it,just passed the tiger heading towards the parrot
look, an island with a parrot on a tree! south-east of the parrot, i see 3 rocks. what's the next move, buddy?
Instead of going toward the three rocks, so around the parrot (right of the stick you just crossed) and go between the parrot and elephant. Then crooss the three rocks until you see a frog
alright. skirting right past the parrot and elephant now
Veo esas tres rocas. dirigiéndose hacia la rana
Great! Now go forward towards the dark green tree but instead turn around from your right side. Go past the yellow-ish tree and cross the alligator and rock until you are by the elephant again
okay, going past the yellow-ish tree and alligator now, towards the elephant again
Once by the elephant, go across the light gray rocks where you will see a giraffe
great! crossing the gray rocks, heading towards this giraffe! what now, pal?
Go along the side of the water until you see the stick cross it and pass the snake and trees. You should see the treasure
perfect! passing the snake and trees
¡Ah, ya lo veo! ¡el tesoro! *terminado* gracias por las instrucciones amigo mío, ¡fue divertido!
hola, q tal? ready to go?
yep
awesome! start by going left. walk past the wooden bench toward the florist stand
sube al sendero, luego gira y regresa por donde viniste. ¡Estamos haciendo un poco de zigzag aquí!
so go backwards on the bridge?
sí, efectivamente, regresa hacia el perrito blanco
We need to lull him a little more!
until what part of the bridge to I walk to before I turn back
vuelve hasta ver de nuevo el banquito de madera
luego, cruzamos el sendero hacia el sur. hay otro perrito blanco esperándonos allí
I am back at the white dog
perfecto! now continue straight down, you should see a red and white checkered picnic mat with our next furry friend
keep going!
I am there
¡excelente! Ahora súbete a la alfombra y continúa hacia el oeste, ¡nuestro pequeño desvío ha terminado! Esté atento a un plato de bayas: lo vamos a pasar.
In english
sorry about that! go over the mat, touch the berry bowl and head west
we're going on a berry slight detour
So I head towards the deer?
not yet my friend, there's another wooden branch that crosses a river to the north
necesitas cruzarlo
Okay I crossed it
brilliant! now avoid the green bush by circling it from the right until you reach the florist stand
Okay
agárra con fuerza la esquina a la izquierda, pasa por debajo del puesto de flores y camina hacia el gran puente
I am at the bridge
perfect! now, just pass the bridge towards the west
you should see two people on a bicycle as you go
done
great! continue past the bridge
¿Ves a la pareja de personas mayores disfrutando de sus periódicos en un banco?
yes
awesome! now just shift southwards, between them and another wooden branch you see
head towards the green bush
done
¡fantástico! Ahora ve hacia el este, la rama y el arbusto deberían estar a cada lado tuyo.
english
no worries! go east, with the branch and bush on either side of you
done
keep going east for a few steps until you spot a young brown deer
¡Ese es nuestro objetivo final!
hola, q tal? ready to go?
yes
sweet! i'm at the tent on top
¿Adónde voy después?
Head south between the rocks and dog
cool, moving south between rocks and dog
now i see a fire, a red mushroom and a blue car. how's next?
curve around the dog so you are between the dog and fire/ Curve again so you go between the fire and mushrooms
Lo tengo, curvado alrededor del perro, ahora moviéndose entre el fuego y el hongo.
Then go as if you are headed to the car but turn around next to the green bush. Then one the path goes into two directions, take the one headed south
alright, heading towards the car, around the green bush
taking the south path now
Then so until you see a curve in the path. Instead of continuing the path go between the telescope and bush
Bien, dejando el camino, caminando entre el telescopio y el arbusto ahora.
Then head west down the path until you see many rock next yo you. Head yoward the rocks and follow them towards a cabin
going west down the path and following rocks to the cabin
hold up, i see the house! *finished* thanks for the awesome guide, pal!
hey, estas listo?
yes
awesome! let's go. head southwest. pass under the first palm tree
move right, cross the second tree. sharp left before the third one. keep walking south. you're doing great!
south and then?
after a few steps, tilt a bit to the left
luego gire nuevamente a la derecha, en dirección sur. ¡Cuidado con el cachorro!
english
my bad, keep moving south but make sure to dodge that brown puppy on your left! turn a bit to your right after that
then
walk forward till you see two rocks: a big one to your left, and a small one to your right
¡Pasa entre ellos para llegar al océano!
I am at the ocean
great, now step into the water
see that big red crab? go right, following the line of the big rock, and keep heading west
I dont understand those directions are opposite
my bad, got a bit twisted there
solo asegúrate de que la gran roca esté a tu lado izquierdo mientras te diriges hacia el oeste
english
oops, sorry about that! just make sure the large rock is on your left as you travel westward
you're doing amazing!
then
after a bit, you'll see a third rock of medium size
solo sigue adelante
then
watch out for the shark and make a swift right turn! all good so far?
yes
awesome! get back to dry land now
Busque una bola azul, amarilla y blanca junto a una roca mediana. camina entre ellos y dirígete hacia el norte
okay
next, veer slightly left and keep going north-west
watch out for a red tent on your left and a big speaker on your right!
okay
¡dulce! Ahora, rodea la tienda y luego dirígete hacia el sur, hacia el mar.
english
oops! my bad again
now, loop around the tent and then head south toward the sea
done
great! now before you hit the water again, take a right turn and walk under a red kayak
sigue avanzando hacia el oeste. ¡Estás haciendo un trabajo increíble!
done
good job! take a sharp right turn going north now, and keep walking alongside that kayak until you reach a small green bush
you're almost there!
